          "id": "400c23a8f25d094865701eb12c3b7bf595c23fb5",
          "message": "feat(tasks): propagate tracing span context to spawned tasks (#112)\n\n* feat(tasks): propagate tracing span context to spawned tasks\n\n- Capture current span context in BlockingTaskPool::spawn\n- Propagate span context in TokioTaskSpawner::spawn_blocking\n- Add tracing dependency to katana-tasks crate\n- Add tests to verify span propagation works correctly\n\nThis ensures database operations in spawned tasks are properly\nnested under RPC request spans instead of appearing orphaned.\n\nCo-Authored-By: karii@cartridge.gg <evergreenkary@gmail.com>\n\n* refactor(tasks): remove span propagation tests\n\nRemove span propagation tests as requested in PR review.\nThe core span context propagation functionality remains intact.\n\nCo-Authored-By: karii@cartridge.gg <evergreenkary@gmail.com>\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: Devin AI <158243242+devin-ai-integration[bot]@users.noreply.github.com>\nCo-authored-by: karii@cartridge.gg <evergreenkary@gmail.com>",
